    <p><strong>How this review was built:</strong> We did not purchase, install, or personally test LeadsMiner Pro. This article is based entirely on independent desk research: the product's own public marketing pages, the MunchEye affiliate-launch listing, third-party review sites, and publicly documented Facebook platform policies. Where a claim could not be independently verified — including all income figures and all performance statistics — we say so explicitly rather than presenting it as fact.</p>
  </Methodology>
