<section id="overview">
  <h2>LeadsMiner Pro Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
  <p>LeadsMiner Pro was launched in September 2025 by Wayne Crowe, who also created the OLSP System (including OLSP Academy). It is sold as a standalone product — a desktop application rather than a web dashboard or training course — and is distributed through a standard affiliate-launch model: listed on MunchEye, promoted by third-party affiliate marketers earning a reported 50% commission throughout the funnel.</p>

  <h3>What's Included</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Post Friender:</strong> scans Facebook posts matching a user-configured niche keyword, collects a list of people who liked, commented on, or reacted to those posts, and sends automated friend requests to them.</li>
    <li><strong>Member Friender:</strong> targets recently active members of specified Facebook groups in the user's niche and sends automated friend requests to them.</li>
    <li><strong>Audience Builder:</strong> organises collected leads into segmented contact lists by niche interest, enabling future outreach campaigns.</li>
    <li><strong>Training videos:</strong> step-by-step onboarding videos covering software setup and configuration, included in the front-end purchase.</li>
    <li><strong>Live sessions (reported):</strong> access to recurring live training sessions with Wayne Crowe — described in marketing as two to three sessions per week via Facebook.</li>
    <li><strong>Optional upsells:</strong> Mass Messenger (DM automation), advanced pipeline tools, mass group-invite features, agency rights, and a CRM layer are reportedly available as separate paid add-ons.</li>
  </ul>

