<section id="history">
  <h2>History &amp; Updates</h2>
  <p>LeadsMiner Pro launched in September 2025, according to its MunchEye affiliate-launch listing. It was created by Wayne Crowe, who publicly describes himself as an online marketer with approximately 15 years of experience and the founder of the OLSP System. LeadsMiner Pro is a separate commercial product from OLSP Academy — it is a desktop software tool, not a training-and-commission platform — but it exists within the same brand ecosystem and is sold to the same general audience of affiliate and digital marketers.</p>
  <p>The connection between the two products is functional as well as commercial: LeadsMiner Pro is designed to build a Facebook friends list of niche-engaged prospects, while OLSP Academy's Mega Link system provides a ready-made monetisation funnel to promote to that same audience. The products can be used independently, but Wayne Crowe's marketing positions them as complementary.</p>
  <Callout type="info">
    <strong>Due-diligence tip:</strong> When a product creator sells multiple tools designed to feed into one another, consider evaluating each product's standalone value before purchasing the combination. A tool that only delivers its claimed results when paired with another paid product from the same creator is worth scrutinising carefully.
