  <h3>Alternatives Worth Comparing</h3>
  <p>Anyone considering LeadsMiner Pro should also evaluate: manual organic outreach (free, compliant, slower), OLSP Academy for a done-for-you affiliate monetisation structure, and Facebook Ads Manager for compliant paid targeting. If the goal is building a sustainable Facebook-based audience, a combination of compliant content strategy and paid advertising carries meaningfully less platform risk than third-party automation. For a broader look at turning Facebook connections into a real audience you own, see our <a href="/blog/build-email-list-affiliate-marketing-no-website/">guide to building an email list for affiliate marketing without a website</a>.</p>
