  <p>After purchasing the front-end product, expect to be presented with a series of OTO (one-time offer) upsell pages before reaching the members area. Declining these upsells will not prevent you from accessing the front-end product you paid for. Be sceptical of countdown timers and "today only" pricing language, which are standard tactics in this category of product launch and do not necessarily indicate a genuine time limit.</p>
