  <FaqItem question="Can a complete beginner use LeadsMiner Pro effectively?" answer="Setup and installation are described as beginner-friendly. However, effective use requires understanding Facebook's niche landscape well enough to configure meaningful keyword and group targets, knowing how many daily actions stay within safe limits, and having a follow-up strategy for newly added connections. A beginner with no existing niche knowledge or Facebook presence is likely to find limited results even if the software installs and runs without issue." />
